      "picks_file": "picks/picks-2026-05-30-1844.md",
      "why_text": "Kelly Curtis, who appeared in films like *The Sentinel* and carried the weight of Hollywood royalty as the daughter of Tony Curtis and Janet Leigh, has died at 69. Though she lived largely outside her famous family's spotlight, her death closes a chapter on a generation of Old Hollywood legacy. Jamie Lee Curtis publicly mourning her sister makes this a rare, raw moment of grief playing out in real time for one of entertainment's most storied families.",
